description:
Discover videos from around the world and create your own with easy-to-use tools to capture your life. 

From your morning coffee to your evening commute, TikTok has the videos to make your day. Whether you’re a sports fanatic, a travel lover or simply looking for a laugh, there’s something for everyone on TikTok. Enjoy an endless stream of short videos on things you love most. Watch what you like, skip what you don’t. 
 
WATCH
A personalised video feed based on what you watch, like, and share. TikTok offers you real, interesting, and fun videos that will make your day.  You'll find a variety of videos from Food and Fashion to Sports and DIY - and everything in between.

 
CREATE
Pause and resume your video with just a tap. As many times as you need.
Millions of creators on TikTok showcase their incredible skills and every day life. Let yourself be inspired.
 
ENTERTAIN
Be entertained and inspired by a global community of creators.

Take video creation to the next level with special effects, filters, music, and more. Unlock filters, effects, and AR objects to take your videos to the next level.
 
CUSTOMISE
Our integrated editing tools allow you to easily edit your videos.
Trim, cut, merge and duplicate video clips without leaving the app.
 
ADD MUSIC
Add your favorite sound to your videos with millions of music clips and sounds. 
We curate music and sound playlists for you with the hottest tracks in every genre, including Hip Hop, EM, Pop, Rock, Rap, and Country, and the most viral original sounds.

Obtain access to LIVE benefits to better interact with hosts!
Choose between a one-month subscription or auto-renewal subscription to enjoy special LIVE benefits (currently only available in limited regions)

Die-hard sports fans, welcome to the app that brings the game right onto your palms, every tick from the game can now be felt in your room. This is the only app that allows for a multi-dimensional experience, keeping you relevant and as a part of the action regardless of your location or your favorite sport, team, or league.

* DRM Sport Key Features *

 - Live Match Insights: Imagine getting score updates instantly whenever the scoring team delivers to the goal, together with crucial events in a match that alters its nature. From first whistle through to final play, follow the drama from beginning to end.

- Comprehensive Match Statistics: Subsequent screenshots show a detailed account of all the statistics a match possesses; shots on target, shots off measures, saves, fouls, corners, offsides, out of more. Go beyond the basic stat lines to explore deeper metrics for a better understanding of the momentum in the game.

- Recent and Upcoming Schedules: Stay uptight with the latest and upcoming events. One can also learn detailed descriptions for the upcoming matches along with recent match results from various leagues and competitions.

- Lineups and Events: Both pre game and during game background information lists regarding active players, along with player changes, cautions, player performance and stat updates for every minute.

- Head-to-Head Analysis: Such stats can be used to formulate strategies for predicting the winner of a game based on team history, performance trends and results of their matches.

- Interactive Point Tables: Look at the tables at the moment and monitor the standings, points, wins, draws and losses. Keep an eye on the battle as your team climbs up the leaderboard.

- Player Profiles: Find out how many goals each individual player has scored, assisted and how many penalties were saved. View history of recent matches and transfers in more depth regarding how players aged and evolved in the sport.

- Match Predictions and Analytics: Make use of sophisticated analytics to witness estimated results that are based on the form of the teams, statistics of players, and past records. Get into match trends for a holistic tactical picture.

- Breaking Sports News: Keep refreshing with appropriate and helpful news articles, exclusive advertisements and opinions. Be the first to know about game changing happenings, player exchange, etc.

- Search and Explore: Use a powerful search tool to locate your favorites teams, leagues, or people. Get games, stats and news that cater to your interests.

Download now to get an experience like never seen before. Be it match details, player information, or breaking news, an anticipation of this app will keep you ahead of the pack.
